blogPosts.blogPostBody: Hey friends! It's been mpossible to stay at home in this sunny weather! Perfect day for a trail! I just need to choose between beach or park....what do you prefer?

blogPostComments.commentBody: You definetly should go to Rockwood Park!
Mispec BEach is so beautiful today! Check out my blog on this topic.

blogPosts.blogPostBody: I highly recommend everybody to read Nelson Wild's latest book. I couldn't stop reading, I can't believe I finished it in just two days! And thanky you Lucas for the recommendation!

blogPostComments.commentBody: Crazy! I have to buy it now.
I'm glad you liked the book. Thank you for the feedback.

blogPosts.blogPostTitle: My Favorite day in the year!
blogPosts.blogPostBody: Today it's my birthday!! I am so happy to celebrate it with my family and friends! Thank You for all the calls and messages.

blogPostComments.commentBody: :( I wish I could be with you today... Happy birthday anyway! I hope you had a great time!
I am glad you liked our little surprise! Happy birthday!

blogPosts.blogPostBody: Best trip ever with the best companies! It was memorable! I can't wait for to plan the next one.

blogPostComments.commentBody: Cool! Let me know when you plan the next one!
OMG! It really was the best trip! Send me the pictures when you have time!

blogPosts.blogPostBody: We couldn't imagine this waterfall was so huge! Astonishing! The pictures do not reflect the magnitude.
OMG! I didn't know each zebra had unique stripes pattern! SO cool! It's like our fingerprints!

blogPostComments.commentBody: Nature is really incredible!

blogPosts.blogPostBody: Please friends, don't let me eat hot food never more! I've just burned my tongue =(

blogPostComments.commentBody: I am really sorry about that. I know it hurts a lot.
Sorry about that
Own dear, I can imagine how it hurts.

blogPosts.blogPostBody: This weekend trip was to Saint Andrews. What a lovely place! You should visit there. Just make sure to go on a sunny day!

blogPostComments.commentBody: My favorite place!
Great!
